    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    CashierController
    Controller for cashier-side operations in the POS system.
    CashierService
    Service layer for cashier-side operations in the POS system.

    Lightweight employee entity used by UI code paths that do not require the full Employee model.
    CashierService.EmployeeData
    DTO representing a single employee row's current UI state.
    CashierView
    Entry point for launching the cashier interface of the POS system.

    Entity class representing a customer in the POS system.
    DatabaseConnection
    Utility class for managing PostgreSQL database connections.
    Employee
    Entity class representing an employee in the POS system.
    HomeController
    Controller for the home screen of the POS system.
    HomeView
    Entry point for launching the home interface of the POS system.

    Entity class representing an inventory item in the POS system.
    Inventory
    Entry point for launching the Inventory view of the POS system.
    InventoryAddDeleteController
    Controller for the Add/Delete Inventory popup in the Manager Dashboard.
    InventoryController
    Controller for the Inventory screen in the POS system.
    ItemController
    Controller for the Item customization view in the cashier interface.
    ManageEmployeeController
    Controller for managing employee records in the POS system.
    ManageEmployeeView
    Entry point for launching the Manage Employee view of the POS system.
    ManagerService
    ManagerService (schema-aligned) ------------------------------- Read-only queries for the Statistics page, aligned with your current DB: "Order" : id, date (timestamp), price (numeric), employeeId (int), customerId (int) "Employee" : id, isManager (bool) "Customer" : id, email (text), points (int) "MenuItem" : id, name (text), price (numeric) "OrderItem" : id, menuItemId, orderId, ...
    ManagerService.OrderDTO
     
    MenuController
    Controller for the Menu Management screen in the POS system.
    MenuItem
    Entity class representing a menu item in the POS system.
    MenuView
    Entry point for launching the Menu view of the POS system.
    NewItemController
    Controller for creating and editing menu items in the POS system.
    NewItemView
    Entry point for launching the New Item view of the POS system.
    Order
    Entity class representing a customer order in the POS system.
    OrderItem
    Entity class representing an individual item within a customer order in the POS system.
    Recipe
    Entity class representing a recipe item in the POS system.
    Statistics
    Entry point for launching the Statistics view of the POS system.
    StatisticsController
    Controller for the manager-facing Order History and Statistics screen.
    StatisticsController.OrderRow
    View-model representing a single order row in the Orders table.
    StatisticsController.PURow
    View-model representing product usage by inventory item for a given period.
    StatisticsController.SalesByItemRow
    View-model representing sales metrics grouped by item (or category).
    StatisticsController.XReportRow
    View-model representing hourly X-Report metrics for a specific day.
    Topping
    Entity class representing a drink topping in the POS system.
    ToppingRecipe
    Entity class representing the relationship between a topping and the inventory items used to create it in the POS system.
